title: Memphis upsets No. 13 Ole Miss 37-24 to stay perfect
text:
> Sports Memphis upsets No. 13 Ole Miss 37-24 to stay perfect Memphis head coach Justin Fuente argues a call with line judge Will McDonald, right, in the second half of an NCAA college football game against Mississippi Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, in Memphis, Tenn. Memphis upset No. 13 Mississippi 37-24. (AP Photo/Mark Humphrey)
